OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1772021939
OL,3,CCasting director who won BAFTA
OL,4,C'incredibly proud' to represent Welsh
OL,5,Cvoices
OL,7,FA Welsh casting director who won a
OL,8,FBAFTA award for her work on the
OL,9,FBritish film 'I Swear' says she is
OL,10,F"incredibly proud" to represent Welsh
OL,11,Fvoices.
OL,13,FLauren Evans, from Hendy in
OL,14,FCarmarthenshire, was announced as the
OL,15,Fwinner in the best casting category at
OL,16,Fthe film awards on Sunday.
OL,18,FEvans has been nominated for this
OL,19,Faward twice in the past and has
OL,20,Fdescribed winning it as a
OL,21,F"sensational" feeling.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/6
