OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1772021939
OL,3,CCasting director who won BAFTA
OL,4,C'incredibly proud' to represent Welsh
OL,5,Cvoices
OL,7,F"It's validation that what I'm doing
OL,8,Fis alright," she told ITV. "Sometimes
OL,9,Fyou have some self-doubt creeping in.
OL,10,FYou feel like an imposter. But it
OL,11,Ffeels like I'm maybe on the right
OL,12,Ftrack."
OL,14,FEvans, who has worked on worldwide
OL,15,Fhits like Netflix' Sex Education and
OL,16,FPaddington 2, spoke of the importance
OL,17,Fof being able to represent Welsh
OL,18,Fvoices through her work, and the
OL,19,Fbarriers she faced getting into the
OL,20,Findustry.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@LO]tD@GO]
