OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1772021939
OL,3,CCasting director who won BAFTA
OL,4,C'incredibly proud' to represent Welsh
OL,5,Cvoices
OL,7,F"I'm so incredibly proud to be Welsh
OL,8,Fand to come from where I'm from, and
OL,9,Fto represent a regional working class
OL,10,Fvoice. Especially in this industry,
OL,11,Fwhere there are barriers to get in.
OL,13,F"As soon as I open my mouth and they
OL,14,Fhear this voice, I think people might
OL,15,Fthink that I'm ditzy or not very good
OL,16,Fat my job. So it means a lot to me,
OL,17,Fand to other Welsh people to see
OL,18,Frepresentation."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUzD@PO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/6
