PN,46404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1772021939
OL,3,CCasting director who won BAFTA
OL,4,C'incredibly proud' to represent Welsh
OL,5,Cvoices
OL,7,FReacting to her win, Lauren said that
OL,8,Freality hadn't "sunk in quite yet" and
OL,9,Fthat it still felt "absolutely mad".
OL,11,F"I had my phone in my lap and I could
OL,12,Fsee it popping off. But I couldn't
OL,13,Freally respond. I'm still trying to
OL,14,Fget through all the messages."
OL,26,@pD@POUpD@bO]sD@AOUvD@^O]
