PN,46405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1772021939
OL,3,CCasting director who won BAFTA
OL,4,C'incredibly proud' to represent Welsh
OL,5,Cvoices
OL,7,FLauren won the BAFTA award for Best
OL,8,FCasting for her work on the film I
OL,9,FSwear, which tells the story of
OL,10,FScottish Tourette's campaigner John
OL,11,FDavidson's life with the condition,
OL,12,Fwhich he developed when he was 12. It
OL,13,Fstars Robert Aramayo, who won best
OL,14,Factor for his performance in the film.
OL,15,FHe was also named EE Rising Star
OL,17,FCasting has only been awarded in the
OL,18,FBAFTAs since 2019, and later this year
OL,19,Fwill be recognised at the Oscars for
OL,20,Fthe first time.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/6
