PN,46406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1772021939
OL,3,CCasting director who won BAFTA
OL,4,C'incredibly proud' to represent Welsh
OL,5,Cvoices
OL,7,F"Casting can make or break the
OL,8,Fproduction," Lauren said, "It's quite
OL,9,Flate in the day that we've had a seat
OL,10,Fat the table. It's not always been
OL,11,Frecognised."
